definitions.definition: Something, usually abnormal , which grows out of something else.
A disfiguring or unwanted mark or adjunct .
The epenthesis of a consonant, e.g., warmth as [ˈwɔrmpθ] (adding a [p] between [m] and [θ]), or -t (Etymology 2) .

main_definition: Something, usually abnormal , which grows out of something else.
